refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;

 arrayini_get_all
 stringextension
 booldetails&true;



 Returns all the registered configuration options.

&reftitle.notes;



  ini_get_all ignores "array" ini options such as
  pdo.dsn.*.

&reftitle.examples;
ini_get_all examples
<?php print_r(ini_get_all("pcre")); print_r(ini_get_all()); ?>
&example.outputs.similar;
